# Supported Platforms

* CentOS 7

# Parameters

* mount:
    mounts(list):
      path(string): Path to the mountpoint
      server:
        name(string): Server to connect to
        path(string): Remove path to mount
      version(int, 3): NFS version to use

* selinux:
    homedirs_on_nfs(bool, False): Allow home directories over NFS
